course_title: Special Topics in Contemporary Journalism - DATA JOURNALISM

sections.comments: This is a module course worth 1.5 credits. Students must have successfully completed JRNL 503 and JRNL 515. The class will run with a minimum enrollment of 12 students.  If the module becomes full, please email jrnl.journal@ubc.ca to be put on the wait list. The class will be conducted online. Please await further instructions from the course instructor closer to the class start date. If the course becomes full, please email jrnl.journal@ubc.ca to be added to the Waitlist.
